# Bloom Path - Delete Your Account

**Effective Date:** July 10, 2026

Bloom Path respects your privacy and gives users the ability to permanently delete their account and associated personal data.

## How to request account deletion

You may request deletion of your account using either of the following methods:

### Option 1 (Recommended)

Open the Bloom Path app and navigate to:

**Profile → Settings → Delete Account**

Follow the on-screen instructions to permanently delete your account.

### Option 2

If you cannot access the app, contact us at:

**support@bloompath.app**

Please include the email address associated with your account.

---

# What data will be deleted

When your request is completed, we permanently delete:

- Parent account
- Child profiles
- Learning progress
- Daily schedules
- Achievement badges
- Rewards
- Game history
- Video progress
- Account preferences

---

# Data we may retain

Some information may be retained when required by law, including:

- Billing records
- Tax records
- Fraud prevention records
- Information required to comply with legal obligations

These records are retained only for the legally required period.

---

# Processing time

Most deletion requests are completed within **30 days**.

